    "body": "This should be fixed in #8832 because sync-data is not modified anymore (it isn't even useful when using rpc which is the only thing that is usable right now in the app). I wonder why only iOS has this issue though, but I think the cause was that sync-data was set to :offline and it is not a case supported by the subtitle for one to one chat which used to display the network syncing status.",
